Sentencas: High catalytic activity PrBaCo2O5+delta (PBC) cathode with impregnated Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-delta (SSC) was investigated as a highly active cathode for intermediate-temperature SOFCs (IT-SOFCs) with BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3-delta (BZCY7) electrolytes.
Titulo: Fabrication and evaluation of Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ impregnated PrBaCo2O5+δ composite cathode for proton conducting SOFCs

Sentencas: The nanoscale impregnated SSC particles were deposited on the surface of the PBC framework.
Titulo: Fabrication and evaluation of Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ impregnated PrBaCo2O5+δ composite cathode for proton conducting SOFCs

Sentencas: The single cell with impregnated SSC cathode was tested from 600 to 700 degrees C with humidified hydrogen (similar to 3% H2O) as the fuel and the static air as the oxidant, and showed higher performance than the cell with pure PBC cathode.
Titulo: Fabrication and evaluation of Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ impregnated PrBaCo2O5+δ composite cathode for proton conducting SOFCs

Sentencas: The results indicated that the impregnation method can be promising ways to improve the catalytic activity of cathode for proton-conducting SOFCs.
Titulo: Fabrication and evaluation of Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ impregnated PrBaCo2O5+δ composite cathode for proton conducting SOFCs
